stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending : dream creates proposal
    pending --> approved : persona approve
    pending --> rejected : persona reject
    approved --> [*]
    rejected --> [*] : rejection_count < 3
    rejected --> [*] : rejection_count = 3 (column blacklisted)

    note right of approved
        Atomic transaction:
        persona row attribute-column
        update + status flip in one step.
    end note

    note left of rejected
        Blacklist is per
        (persona_slug, attribute_column)
        and enforced as a dream-side
        guard, not a state.
    end note
